@host = http://localhost:8080

### Login — devuelve el token (admin@papaws.com / consultas@papaws.com / rescatistas@papaws.com)
# @name login
POST {{host}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@papaws.com",
  "password": "papaws123"
}

###
@token = {{login.response.body.token}}

### Salud (público)
GET {{host}}/api/salud

### Rescatistas (lectura: cualquier rol)
GET {{host}}/api/rescatistas
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Animales (lectura: cualquier rol)
GET {{host}}/api/animales
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Crear rescatista (Administrador o EncargadoRescatistas)
POST {{host}}/api/rescatistas
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nombreCompleto": "Ana Pérez",
  "telefonoContacto": "099123456",
  "correoElectronico": "ana@papaws.com",
  "organizacion": "ONG",
  "zonaOperacion": "Norte"
}

### Crear animal (Administrador o EncargadoRescatistas)
POST {{host}}/api/animales
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nombre": "Toto",
  "especie": "Loro",
  "pesoActual": 0.45,
  "rescatistaId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000"
}

###
